WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
 IK10 - Sony Vandal-Resistance for Security Cameras 

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:33.000
 24 hours a day, 365 days a year, security cameras are required to keep working properly even under difficult conditions. 

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:46.000
 Sony offers iK10-resistant network cameras. 

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:58.000
 International classification IK shows the degree of protection against external shock. 

00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:20.000
 The IK10 rated camera can withstand an external shock worth 20 joules. 

00:01:28.000 --> 00:02:02.000
 Security cameras must work up: Attack on the camera before proceeding to steal cars Subversive vandalism in the school campus Intruder in the warehouse tries to avoid detection Violent violent raid on the ATM 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:16.000
 Even in the toughest monitoring environments, Sony has the answer. 

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:22.000
 Sony does not guarantee that its cameras can withstand multiple hits with a hammer. 

